'''核纖層'''旧称“'''核周层'''”、“'''核衬层'''”或“'''核层'''”，是位于[[细胞核|细胞核]]内[[染色质|染色质]]与[[核膜|核膜]]之间的高[[电子密度|电子密度]]网络片层结构，<ref>{{Cite book | author = Alberts B, Johnson A, Lewis J, et al. | title = Molecular Biology of the Cell (4<sup>th</sup> edition) | location = New York | publisher = Garland Science | date = 2002 | pages = 676-677 | ISBN = 0-8153-3218-1 | accessdate = 2011 | url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK21054/ | language = en | quote =  | archive-date = 2019-09-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190919002941/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK21054/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>由[[中间丝|中间丝]]与[[膜相关蛋白|膜相关蛋白]]（membrane associated proteins）交织形成，普遍存在于[[真核细胞|真核细胞]]的细胞核中。核纤层处于[[核基质|核基质]]中，在核内与[[核内膜|核内膜]]（inner nuclear membrane，INM）相连，在核外则与[[内质网|内质网]]相连。<ref>{{cite journal | author = 王虎 | year = 2002 | month =  | day =  | title = 核纤层蛋白Lamins的结构、功能及相关疾病的研究 | journal = 中国分子心脏病学杂志 | volume =  | issue = 4 | pages =  | pmid =  | doi =  | url = http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTOTAL-ZGFB200204012.htm | language = zh-hans | access-date = 2011-04-17 | archive-date = 2019-09-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190918134724/http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTOTAL-ZGFB200204012.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>核纤层是支撑细胞核的一种结构，<ref>{{cite journal | author = 蔡树涛、翟中和 | year = 1990 | month =  | day =  | title = Nuclear Lamina(核纤层)——一种重要的细胞核结构 | journal = 细胞生物学杂志 | volume =  | issue = 1 | pages =  | pmid =  | doi =  | url = http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTOTAL-XBZZ199001003.htm | language = zh-hans | access-date = 2011-04-17 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064929/http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTOTAL-XBZZ199001003.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>对调节[[DNA自我复制|DNA自我复制]]、[[DNA转录|DNA转录]]、[[细胞凋亡|细胞凋亡]]与[[细胞分裂|细胞分裂]]过程中核膜的破裂及重建也起到一定作用。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Goldman RD, Gruenbaum Y, Moir RD,Shumaker DK, Spann TP | title = Nuclear lamins: building blocks of nuclear architecture. | journal = Genes Dev. | volume = 16 | issue = 5 | pages = 533-547 | pmid = 11877373 | doi =  | url = http://biology.buffalo.edu/Faculty/Yu/lecture_material/Lecture1/Goldman_02_NuclearLamin.pdf | language = en | date = Mar 1, 2002 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100611191026/http://biology.buffalo.edu/Faculty/Yu/lecture_material/Lecture1/Goldman_02_NuclearLamin.pdf | archivedate = 2010-06-11 }}</ref>此外，核纤层还可以辅助组织染色质并锚定[[核孔复合物|核孔复合物]]（nuclear pore complexes，NPCs）、[[核膜蛋白|核膜蛋白]]及[[转录因子|转录因子]]。

